wmau-site-full-title: Full title of the site (sometimes different from sitetitle). {{notranslate}}
wmau-site-email: Email address to be displayed in the site footer. {{notranslate}}
wmau-footer-blurb: Wikitext for the site footer. Empty by default.
wmau-logo-wordmark-alt: Image alt text for the logo's wordmark.
wmau-logo-icon-alt: Image alt text for the logo's icon.
wmau-talk-link: Link text for subject-page footer link to the talk page.
wmau-subject-link: Link text for talk-page header link back to the subject page.
